com.connectsdk.core

Class MediaInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.connectsdk.core.MediaInfo

  • public class MediaInfo
extends Object
    Normalized reference object for information about a media to display. This object can be used to pass as a parameter to displayImage or playMedia.
